Package simu.model

Class ServicePoint

java.lang.Object
simu.model.ServicePoint
public class ServicePoint extends Object
The class ServicePoint represents a service point in the simulation model. The service point has a queue of orders and serves the orders in the queue.

    • ServicePoint

      public ServicePoint(ContinuousGenerator generator, EventList eventList, EventType type)
      Creates a new service point with the given generator, event list and event type.
      Parameters:
      generator - The generator for the service times.
      eventList - The event list where new events are added.
      type - The type of the event that is scheduled when starting a new service.

  • Method Details

    • addToQueue

      public void addToQueue(Order a)
      Adds an order to the end of the queue. The first order in the queue is the one being served.
      Parameters:
      a - The order to be added to the queue.

      Removes the first order from the queue and returns it.

      The first order in the queue.

    • serve

      public void serve()
      Starts a new service for the first order in the queue. Returns the first order in the queue without removing it.

    • isBusy
